    "url": "data/movies.json"
  },
  "mark": "point",
  "encoding": {
    "x": {
      "field": "Rotten Tomatoes Rating",
      "type": "quantitative",
      "axis": {"title": "Rotten Tomatoes Rating"}
    },
    "y": {
      "field": "Worldwide Gross",
      "type": "quantitative",
      "axis": {"title": "Worldwide Gross ($)"}
    }
  }
}
```

**Narrative**: By mapping ratings to earnings, this plot helps determine how critical acclaim might influence a movie’s financial performance worldwide.

### 4. **Changes in Movie Release Dates Over Time**

**Objective**: Analyze historical trends in movie releases annually.

#### Visualization Specification:
```json
{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
  "description": "Line chart showing the number of movies released each year.",
  "data": {
    "url": "data/movies.json"
  },
  "transform": [
    {"calculate": "year(datum['Release Date'])", "as": "Release Year"},
    {"aggregate": [{"op": "count", "as": "Number of Movies"}], "groupby": ["Release Year"]}
  ],
  "mark": "line",
  "encoding": {
    "x": {
      "field": "Release Year",
      "type": "temporal",
      "title": "Year"
    },
    "y": {
      "field": "Number of Movies",
      "type": "quantitative",
      "title": "Number of Movies Released"
    }
  }
}
```

**Narrative**: This line chart captures the ebb and flow of movie releases over the decades, offering insights into how the industry has evolved in response to various economic, technological, and cultural factors.

---

By integrating these visualizations, we construct a comprehensive narrative that touches upon key elements of the movie industry, providing a detailed look at how various factors intersect to shape the landscape of film production and distribution.

